<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sv">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Projekt | Arik Ben-Shabat</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0a0a0a;
      --bg-2: #121212;
      --surface: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      --text: #f3f4f6;
      --muted: #a1a1aa;
      --accent: #7dd3fc;
      --accent-2: #a78bfa;
    }
    body.light {
      --bg: #e5e7eb;
      --bg-2: #d1d5db;
      --surface: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      --border: rgba(15,23,42,0.10);
      --text: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;
      --accent: #0369a1;
      --accent-2: #7c3aed;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg), var(--bg-2));
    }
    .wrap { width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; }
    .topbar {
      position: sticky; top: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .topbar-inner {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      gap: 12px; padding: 16px 0; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .nav { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .nav a, .theme-toggle {
      padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;
    }
    .theme-toggle { cursor: pointer; }
    main { padding: 40px 0 60px; }
    h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .lead { color: var(--muted); max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 22px;
    }
    .tag-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 14px; }
    .tag {
      padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(125,211,252,0.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(125,211,252,0.20);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    p { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
    @media (max-width: 800px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="wrap topbar-inner">
      <strong>Arik Ben-Shabat</strong>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="index.html">Hem</a>
        <a href="projects.html">Projekt</a>
        <a href="courses.html">Kurser</a>
        <a href="about.html">Om mig</a>
        <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" type="button">Växla tema</button>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="wrap">
    <h1>Projekt</h1>
    <p class="lead">Ett urval av projekt inom AI, optimering, språk och produktivitet.</p>

    <div class="grid">
      <section class="card">
        <h2>QAOA Meeting Scheduler</h2>
        <p>Avancerat schemaläggningssystem med ICS-uppladdning, vikter, constraints och omkörningslogik.</p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">QAOA</span>
          <span class="tag">Scheduling</span>
          <span class="tag">Flask</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>Language Compliance RAG</h2>
        <p>Lokalt RAG-system för att kontrollera språk, ton och formulering mot godkända organisationsdokument.</p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">RAG</span>
          <span class="tag">LLM</span>
          <span class="tag">Compliance</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>AI Recruitment Coordinator</h2>
        <p>AI-stöd för rekryteringsprocesser med tidslinjer, sammanfattning, dokumentstöd och notifieringar.</p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">Automation</span>
          <span class="tag">Streamlit</span>
          <span class="tag">Workflow</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>Semantic Email Assistant</h2>
        <p>Semantisk sökning, klustring och summering av svenska studentmail.</p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">SBERT</span>
          <span class="tag">spaCy</span>
          <span class="tag">NLP</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script>
    if (localStorage.getItem('theme') === 'light') {
      document.body.classList.add('light');
    }
    document.getElementById('themeToggle').addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.body.classList.toggle('light');
      localStorage.setItem('theme', document.body.classList.contains('light') ? 'light' : 'dark');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
